{"about_the_game":"Once upon a time, the land of Raine was renowned for its jewellery craftsmanship, and its landscapes could impress any visitor. But one day, in the afterlife, a fierce fight broke out between demons for the right to the throne. A rift in the afterlife opened up right in the middle of Raine, causing the entire place to fall into ruin. The rift scourge was so powerful that the surviving inhabitants of the area were forever unable to use normal magic \u2013 from then on, they could only wield the magic of demons. Now the Silver Cats guild is trying to restore the world to its former state, and the guild master's son has been chosen as one of those who can restore peace.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> current version of the game: <strong>v1.2</strong><br></li><li> 150 different quests<br></li><li> over 250 crafting recipes<br></li><li> over 1000 different items<br></li><li> 3 types of weapons: one-handed sword, two-handed sword, magic artifact<br></li><li> 4 types of armor: cloth, plate, leather-physical and leather-magic<br></li><li> no binding to character class<br></li><li> 27 locations<br></li><li> 6 levels of difficulty that change the gameplay of your choice<br></li><li> on high difficulty it is necessary to use sharpening, inlay and engraving<br></li><li> 10+ hours of passage on &quot;Researcher&quot; difficulty<br></li><li> 30+ hours of passage on &quot;God&quot; difficulty<br></li><li> no donation</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Silver Cats v1.3 - Early Beta</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1472320/extras/Silver_Cats_v1-3_Early_Beta.jpg?t=1730743916\" /><br>Join in testing the big Silver Cats v1.3 update, which includes new graphics, Steam achievements, updated characters, and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Planned Stages of Silver Cats v1.3 Update</strong></h2>\u2611 Environment (graphics of plants, objects, locations)<br>\u2610 Characters (graphics of NPCs, monsters, bosses, main character, equipment)<br>\u2610 Combat system (new non-targeting system, enemy and main character animations)<br>\u2610 Interface update (design and graphics)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1472320/extras/Beta_Screenshot.jpg?t=1730743916\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Installing the Early Beta of Silver Cats v1.3</strong></h2>All owners of the game can join the test. To take part in testing, you need to go to the game properties in Steam and in the &quot;Betas&quot; section select the branch \u2018v1-3_beta\u2019, after that you can start downloading.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1472320/extras/Beta_Install.jpg?t=1730743916\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Guild Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/a13467dce9cb5daa58e0608d57552f7f18e4ee51.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Item","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/a10e0e551bec231f881a7de1ce0df3689af77d54.jpg"},{"name":"Alchemist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/dfff15610884215d3fd7315240934d63fbc32a70.jpg"},{"name":"Tailor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/59a0c6b4e191a6b5f4508be3b9fa61f7860d4168.jpg"},{"name":"Blacksmith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/c93c90ff203e5f185fdbb6b186c76a4a2484cf0f.jpg"},{"name":"Jeweler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/f0a950c5bb4582f52cc37edf08f875f0429b9f3f.jpg"},{"name":"Chef","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1472320/c718e390adf6e3cbcbf9515ef329da06068c0fe8.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Silver Cat","path":"https://cdn.akamai